Dear Li Ming,
  Hubei University has given you an acceptance letter, which makes me feel pleasure. Congratulations! 
  It is the fact that enough knowledge has been strenuously studied by you since childhood. HuBei University is one of the best campus in China where you can not only enroll but also choose the math that you used to prefer as your major. All of these things make me feel extremely glad for you. 
  There are loads of suggestions to you on how to get prepared for university life. For my perspective, learning becomes more and more important as you get older. Moreover, The prospective work of you should be decided as soon as possible after you know yoursel in the university life.
  Hope you can enjoy your wonderful time in your university.
